The car with VIN- KM8J3CA24HU407087 , (2017 HYUNDAI TUCSON LIMITED AWD 4dr 1.6L) is under customer ANISH OOMMEN and there was engine light on. Contract W-179782
The engine light came on 3  times our Hyundai technician inspected the car and found the following:-
First time:
Cause- IDLE AIR CONTROL SYSTEM MAL.
Fix- SCANTEST CODE P0507 IDLE AIR CONTROL SYSTEM-RPM HIGHER THAN EXPECTED. CHECKED INTAKE SYSTEM NO FAULT FOUND AT THIS TIME.CHECKED AND FOUND UPDATE FOR THIS CODE 646. TL1.6T-GDI P0507  DTC IMPROVEMENT.(ECM). UPDATED ECM.
Second time:
Cause- code p0507 keeps coming back

Third time:
Cause- dual clutch transmission.
Fix - OPENED HYTECH CASE AND THEY SAY IF CLUTCHES ARE WORN OUT IT COULD GIVE THIS CODE. SUGGESTED TO REPLACED DUAL CLUTCH TRANSMISSION.
Now the technician is calling the transmission replacement, the quotes is attached. Customer wants to get the repairs done under the Canada General Warranty, please provide the authorisation number when approved. Looking forward to hear from you.
Regards,
